      "releaseNotes": "Streaks 11.1:\n\n* Added: Halloween themes\n* Added: Extra note to indicate medications task doesn't record to Health\n* Added: New task sort screen\n* Changed: Dots widget now says \"All Done\" instead of \"0 Remaining\"\n* Fixed: Danish translations for state of mind recording\n* Fixed: Pin button may fail on notes screen\n* Fixed: Energy Deficit may show incorrect target on Apple Watch\n\n----\n\nIf you have any issues, feedback or comments, please contact support@streaks.app.",
